high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left, go forward until you reach the wall, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the fork on the table, behind the knife.
Turn left, go straight, turn right, and then go straight to the sink.
Clean the fork in the sink.
Turn right, go forward, turn right, go straight until you reach the wall, then turn right to face the table.
Put the fork on the plate, on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step, then turn left and cross the room, then turn left and face the side of the table
Pick up the fork that is sitting on the table above the knife
Head to the sink that is on your left
Place the fork in the sink  behind the cup and apple and turn on the faucet. Turn off the faucet and pick up the fork
Turn right and cross the room, then left and cross the room, the turn to face the side of the white table
Place the fork on the table on top of the dirty, black plate
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork on a dirty plate

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the side of the white table where the lettuce is.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink.
Place the fork in the sink, wash, and pick back up.
Turn right and walk back to the white table and approach the opposite side as previously.
Put a fork on the brown plate on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Clean a fork and put it on the plate on the table.
